languages.text: "Мы все расскажем, только не губите! Мы знаем, откуда взялась болезнь!"
"We'll tell you everything, just please, spare our lives! We know where the disease came from!"

languages.original_text: "We'll tell you everything, just please, spare our lives! We know where the disease came from!"

languages.text: «Se lo contaremos todo, ¡pero tenga compasión! ¡Sabemos de dónde viene la enfermedad!».
languages.original_text: "We'll tell you everything, just please, spare our lives! We know where the disease came from!"

languages.text: 「すべて話しますから、どうか命だけは…！病気の元凶を知っているんです！」
languages.original_text: "We'll tell you everything, just please, spare our lives! We know where the disease came from!"

traits.locale_text: 「すべて話しますから、どうか命だけは…！病気の元凶を知っているんです！」

languages.text: "Wir erzählen Euch alles, aber bitte verschont unser Leben! Wir wissen, wo die Krankheit hergekommen ist!"
languages.original_text: "We'll tell you everything, just please, spare our lives! We know where the disease came from!"

languages.text: « On vous dira tout, mais je vous en supplie, épargnez-nous ! On sait d'où vient la maladie ! »
